    Serializable, Comparable<ConfigMetaType>, ArgValueValidator

    public enum ConfigMetaType
extends Enum<ConfigMetaType>
implements ArgValueValidator

    Title: ConfigMetaType

    Description: Defines the recognized meta types for command line argument values
